1. create an app

    python manage.py startapp accounts

2. create templates:

    (folder) template => (folder) accounts => dashboard.html, login.html, register.html

3. create url.py in (folder) accounts (not the one in templates)

4. add urlpatterns to (project folder) btre => urls.py:
         path('accounts/', include(accounts.urls)),

4. register app in (folder) btre => settings.py:
    INSTALLED_APPS = [ 
        ...,
        'accounts.apps.AccountsConfig', ]

5. in views.py, define the routes -- import 'redirect'